      "text": "// state mirrors index.State for reading the marker file in `stats`.\ntype state struct {\n\tCommit     string `toml:\"commit\"`\n\tFileCount  int    `toml:\"fileCount\"`\n\tChunkCount int    `toml:\"chunkCount\"`\n}",
